OpenClaw is your own personal AI assistant framework.
Running locally on your Raspberry Pi 5, it allows you to automate tasks, manage files, and interact with various AI models while maintaining full sovereignty over your data.
- Built-in Browser Automation
- Parallel Task Execution
- Multi-platform Messaging (Telegram/WhatsApp)
- Self-Healing Architecture
- Native Desktop Control (xdotool/wmctrl)
- Full Internet Connectivity & Messaging
